# Domains resolved at firewall-init time (A records added to the ipset).
# One domain per line. Blank lines and `#` comments are ignored.
# See init-firewall.sh for CDN-pool CIDRs (allowed-ips.list) and live-fetched
# ranges (GitHub meta, AWS ip-ranges, Google goog.json).

